I look forward to reading the transcript of the call between @realDonaldTrump and Ukraine. Unfortunately, no amount of transparency will satisfy Democrats, who have so desperately searched for a mythical smoking gun to impeach a president they have harassed since his election.

Chemical abortions kill an unborn child & pose major health risks to the mother, like severe bleeding, infection, & even death. I will continue to support the health of all individuals & fight to protect the sanctity of life, beginning at conception & ending in a natural death.

I am proud to be an original cosponsor on @boblatta's SAVE Moms and Babies Act, which would prevent the FDA from loosening the current restrictions on chemical abortions and would prohibit these dangerous drugs from being distributed remotely, by mail or telemedicine.

Today on #NationalPOWMIARecognitionDay, I am proud to join @RepAlLawsonJr in introducing the National POW/MIA Memorial and Museum Act, which would designate the POW/MIA Memorial at Cecil Field in Jacksonville as the National POW/MIA Memorial and Museum. https://rutherford.house.gov/media/press-releases/rutherford-lawson-introduce-bill-establish-national-powmia-memorial-and-museum …

I was honored to work closely with @sandyhook on my STOP School Violence Act. This landmark legislation has already resulted in $175 million to local communities to implement early intervention programs, better connect law enforcement & administrators, & secure our schools.

Great news for Florida! The House just passed, with my support, two bills to prevent drilling in federal waters off Florida’s coast. Offshore drilling harms military readiness, our pristine beaches & our state’s tourism-based economy, & I am pleased to see these bills advance.
